      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Drive away in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well cared for, offering a smooth and reliable ride for its next owner. While there are a few minor signs of previous adventures, it still looks great and performs beautifully on the road. It\u2019s the perfect blend of quality and value for anyone seeking a dependable, high-quality car!",
